In order to enable Portainer, the docker-compose.yml and site.conf for Nginx must be modified.

1. 



ghost:
      image: ghost:alpine
      restart: always
      volumes:
        - ./data/conf/ghost/content:/var/lib/ghost/content
      environment:
        - url=http://www.sharezen.de
      dns:
        - ${IPV4_NETWORK:-172.22.1}.254
      networks:
        mailcow-network:
          aliases:
            - ghost
